{"tid":682864,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] I am just a girl, I’m always ME","createTime":"2018-05-29T08:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T16:02:25.000Z","uid":82917,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"df1f481df5797ef1868391243bf0d3529a780b68","tid":682864,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/155102_f66b09795f8bdfb49c2a3988c3188f5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F155102_f66b09795f8bdfb49c2a3988c3188f5e.png&h=ae9f6c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擁有中五學歷的出爐視后唐屍詠，<br />\n向來閒時喜於在社交媒體上分享感受，<br />\n今日，佢再次向網友們大曬自創英文金句！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢用高難度詞彙x2046講出作為女孩既痛楚，<br />\n並希望得到各界諒解及支持。<br />\n睇完篇野後，情感豐富的小美我也忍不住落淚了。。<br />\n<br />\n就算係好似屍詠咁pure又true，堪稱完美既女生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都會有犯錯既一刻！！！<br />\n都會傷心難過！！！<br />\n尤其被誤解係女同事上台拎獎時西面，<br />\n又或者被指瘋狂利用前度炒作新聞。<br />\n面對呢啲既不實的指控，<br />\n屍詠，選擇了沈默。<br />\n懂她的人自然會懂！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">她，只是，一個，女生。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>I am always me</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/105450_0865a7b5ea75a6ef9df4a0ab47f8a4b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F105450_0865a7b5ea75a6ef9df4a0ab47f8a4b1.png&h=a6e0da95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屍詠：唔好再挑剔我啦！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Credit to 過氣youtuber 大佬B</span>"},{"pid":"f1522b6a57e22f39ec8818ead6ed8279350386e0","tid":682864,"uid":174115,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"37歲仲girl？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係Auntie</span>"},{"pid":"4ef323093d64e402375910bd22620651e673442e","tid":682864,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/104623_7dffa1e1b2f598ce8f2227dcaca958d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F104623_7dffa1e1b2f598ce8f2227dcaca958d0.png&h=83b70422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出道多年的屍詠在面對小朋友時仍充滿童真，稚氣未脫的可愛模樣，實屬難得可見。"},{"pid":"a02750fbdab0c521576be24c1a8eedecee4a770a","tid":682864,"uid":82917,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/105901_40375b2dd9d198f307917334da5b27d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F105901_40375b2dd9d198f307917334da5b27d7.png&h=a526ab2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n視后演技大爆發的一刻！！！其精湛演出贏得眾人眼淚！！！"},{"pid":"ccaff7d6251947260498bfe506a8a94cd2d69d80","tid":682864,"uid":174115,"like":5,"dislike":5,"s